query:
SELECT 
  j.id as jobId, 
  j.customerId as jobCustomerId, 
  j.customerEmail,
  u.id as userId,
  u.email as userEmail
FROM jobs j
LEFT JOIN users u ON u.email = '12@customer.com'
WHERE j.customerEmail = '12@customer.com'
LIMIT 1;
